g.title: j3669351481
g.text: There's something I need to tell you.

g.title: j1218940267
g.text: When you arrived, I figured you were just another obstacle.

g.title: j1230703384
g.text: Ugh. I've been trying to figure out how to do this for *days* now.

g.title: j4206949223
g.text: Just more bullshit for me to overcome, like everything else in my life.

g.title: j2139115246
g.text: Are you breaking up with me...?

g.title: j4067070255
g.text: If you had told me, that day we first crossed swords... how you would go on to change my life?

g.title: j1105417351
g.text: What?! NO! How would that even --

g.title: j2138867478
g.text: No! No. Absolutely not. I'm just...shit at expressing this kind of thing.

g.title: j2307575722
g.text: That you'd save my life? That you'd save ALL our lives?!

g.title: j2566804383
g.text: When you arrived, I figured you were just another obstacle.

g.title: j4255510795
g.text: I'd have laughed in your sodding face.

g.title: j1964027973
g.text: I don't even want to know.

g.title: j2673509259
g.text: Just more bullshit for me to overcome, like everything else in my life.

g.title: j2790251737
g.text: ...... I am *really trying* to have a serious moment here...

g.title: j793849653
g.text: If you had told me, that day we first crossed swords...how you would go on to change my life?

g.title: j1795216411
g.text: That you'd save my life? That you'd save ALL our lives?!

g.title: j2673335590
g.text: There are very few times in your life you meet someone who understands you instinctually.

g.title: j2650595944
g.text: I'd have laughed in your sodding face.

g.title: j3103635409
g.text: Who gets you almost better than you get yourself.

g.title: j3036675622
g.text: And I'm not talking about the obvious -Albrecht and the Major and all the rest of that nonsense.

g.title: j270251517
g.text: Who knows how to tell you what you need to hear, not what you want to hear.

g.title: j1869767259
g.text: I'm talking about something much more important. I'm talking about what you've meant to *me.*

g.title: j1262092076
g.text: What I'm trying to tell you is - thanks for being not just a friend, but being someone I can trust.

g.title: j3963391045
g.text: Shit. I. Sol above, I don't know how to say this.

g.title: j3948751350
g.text: Not just to watch my back, not just to join the team, but... someone I can trust with my life.

g.title: j244665879
g.text: I think I know what you're going to say. Want me to go first?

g.title: j4102134553
g.text: You're making me fall asleep over here.

g.title: j4002265564
g.text: I'm *still* not forgiving you for that spaghetti, though.

g.title: j2902753089
g.text: That...means a lot, thanks Arthur. And it's mutual.

g.title: j4130249611
g.text: Yeah, I've just been fooling you this whole time. Sorry.

g.title: j3427059522
g.text: I think we should just be friends. [Break up.]

g.title: j4267936347
g.text: I'm sorry it took so long to admit it. But I'm glad you're here. We'd all be dead without you.

g.title: j1987067909
g.text: I never thought it was possible.

g.title: j1225890948
g.text: I never thought it was possible.

g.title: j4245101344
g.text: Not like this. Not in a place like this.

g.title: j298652782
g.text: Not like this. Not in a place like this.

g.title: j4053353252
g.text: And certainly not for someone like me.

g.title: j2643306465
g.text: And certainly not for someone like me.

g.title: j1013244585
g.text: And whatever life brings our way?

g.title: j348889670
g.text: This was a mistake. We're done.

g.title: j1698300887
g.text: I know we'll handle it. Together.

g.title: j2721693853
g.text: Better to end things now than to let things get more complicated.

g.title: j871956120
g.text: Time you learned sometimes your sense of humour isn't welcome.

g.title: j66899518
g.text: I thought this kind of happiness wasn't possible for me.

g.title: j1078323548
g.text: If you change your mind, I...I'll be here, love.

g.title: j3454700112
g.text: Thank you for showing me I was wrong, love.
